FIG. 14 is a perspective view showing the communication devices of FIG. 13 in the stacked configuration;


FIG. 15 is a top plan view of the stacked cards of FIG. 14;


FIG. 16 is a rear elevation view of the stacked cards of FIG. 14;


FIG. 17 is a perspective view of a portion of a host system having a PCMCIA slot, showing the stacked communication device of FIG. 14 fully inserted therein;


